<section class="guia-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="guia-intro__content">
      <div class="guia-intro__text">
        <h2 class="guia-intro__title">El Arte de Elegir tu Fragancia</h2>
        <p class="guia-intro__description">
          Elegir un perfume es una experiencia personal y única. Cada fragancia cuenta una historia, 
          evoca recuerdos y refleja tu personalidad. En esta guía, te ayudaremos a descubrir el 
          lenguaje de los perfumes y a encontrar tu aroma ideal.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="guia-intro__stats">
        <div class="guia-intro__stat">
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-number">7</div>
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-label">Familias Olfativas</div>
        </div>
        <div class="guia-intro__stat">
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-number">3</div>
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-label">Notas del Perfume</div>
        </div>
        <div class="guia-intro__stat">
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-number">5</div>
          <div class="guia-intro__stat-label">Concentraciones</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.guia-intro {
  padding: 120px 0;
  background: #fff;
}

.guia-intro__content {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

.guia-intro__text {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto 80px;
}

.guia-intro__title {
  font-size: 48px;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 0 0 30px;
  color: #2d2d2d;
  font-family: 'PP Editorial New', Georgia, serif;
}

.guia-intro__description {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #666;
  margin: 0;
}

.guia-intro__stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 60px;
  text-align: center;
}

.guia-intro__stat {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.guia-intro__stat:hover {
  transform: translateY(-10px);
}

.guia-intro__stat-number {
  font-size: 64px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #667eea;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-family: 'PP Editorial New', Georgia, serif;
}

.guia-intro__stat-label {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #2d2d2d;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .guia-intro {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }
  
  .guia-intro__title {
    font-size: 36px;
  }
  
  .guia-intro__stats {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Guía Intro",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
